languages.text: "Я разложила Его Таро, и расклад сулит опасность. Подумай тщательно, куда ты влечешь Домин, ксенос".
languages.translation_comment:
Speaker Kibellah
Yrliet: "Time is of the essence, elantach — the sooner we go to meet the survivors from Crudarach, the better their chances of avoiding another disaster..."

languages.text: "I have laid out His Tarot, and the spread promises danger. Think carefully where you are leading the Domin, xenos."
